          "date": "2015-06-08 07:43:56.000000000",
          "tz": 480
        },
        "subject": "LU-3270 statahead: refactor statahead code",
        "message": "LU-3270 statahead: refactor statahead code\n\n* statahead thread should wait for async stat RPCs to finish\n  before quit.\n* simplify sai refcounting:\n  - a refcount is taken in allocation, and will be put after\n    starting statahead thread.\n  - statahead thread holds one refcount.\n  - AGL thread holds one refcount.\n  - 'stat' process takes refcount before revalidating dentry against\n    statahead cache.\n* sa_entry is not refcounted because only scanner can remove it\n  from statahead cache.\n* add 'lli_sa_enabled' to indicate whether statahead is enabled for\n  a directory, it will be cleared upon failure or directory close.\n* many smallfixes and cleanups.\n\nThis is a backport to 2.5, because other changes between master\nand 2.5 cause lots of conflicts, 5 statahead patches are backported\nas one:\nLustre-Change: http://review.whamcloud.com/9663\nLustre-commit: I55a4fe66a5f6c04595d3bc84f0cd3750f20e0ee4\nLustre-Change: http://review.whamcloud.com/9664\nLustre-commit: Ibd55227f4c0710139bd039a4e7232dc1cb5041be\nLustre-Change: http://review.whamcloud.com/9665\nLustre-commit: Ife50396dc16beaad921751b4bdd7da721dfc15c9\nLustre-Change: http://review.whamcloud.com/9666\nLustre-commit: I5bc00ddd1a501b94cdfe7509ddb0e7d922bef624\nLustre-Change: http://review.whamcloud.com/9667\nLustre-commit: I65759c7dfcbe879b42f14152dbfe5949e3d37ea0\n\nSigned-off-by: Lai Siyao <lai.siyao@intel.com>\nChange-Id: Ie2fbdc2c9b14c31720e66903a3495d61bf6ba6d5\n"
      },
